11th Avenue, north across W. 50th Street. Note the Gottfried Baking Company plant at the left, the gas station in the foreground and the new taxpayer at the N. E. corner of 50th Street, and compare with photo of same, one year earlier.
View 2 shows details of the aforementioned taxpayer. The Hanscom Bakery maintained a retail surplus store in the building that formerly stood here.
